A simple and robust C++ library for rational and matrix arithmetics,
suitable for scientific applications. See maintest.cpp as en example
for its usage. Or use doxygen to generate documentation about the API.

The library is licenced under the Apache 2.0 license. See LICENSE.txt and
http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
for more details.

The author of the library is Jernej Kovacic (jkovacic AT gmail DOT com).
